   <title type="text">Ge'ez Grammars Online</title>
   <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="tr_bq"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/Ge'ez%20Grammars%20Online%20One%20can%20easily%20fit%20all%20of%20the%20Ge'ez%20grammars%20that%20have%20ever%20been%20published%20in%20European%20languages%20on%20one%20shelf.%20%20Or,%20if%20you%20want%20to%20save%20some%20of%20that%20shelf%20space%20for%20your%20Wheel%20of%20Time%20novels,%20you%20can%20put%20most%20of%20those%20grammars%20on%20a%20flash%20drive/memory%20stick%20instead.%20%20Here%20are%20some%20of%20the%20Ge'ez%20grammars%20that%20are%20available%20as%20PDFs%20(or%20in%20the%20google%20books%20reader)%20online:%20%20Cha%C3%AEne,%20Marius.%20%20Grammaire%20%C3%A9thiopienne.%201907.%20%20Dillman,%20August%20&amp;%20Carl%20Bezold.%20Trans.%20James%20A.%20Chrichton.%20%20Ethiopic%20Grammar.%20%201907.%20%20Dillman,%20August.%20Grammatik%20der%20%C3%A4thiopischen%20Sprache.%201857.%20%20Dillman,%20August%20&amp;%20Carl%20Bezold.%20Grammatik%20der%20%C3%A4thiopischen%20Sprache.%201899.%20%20Ludolf,%20Hiob.%20Grammatica%20aethiopica.%201661.%20%20Mercer,%20Samuel.%20Ethiopic%20Grammar,%20with%20Chrestomathy%20and%20Glossary.%201920.%20%20Praetorius,%20Franz.%20%20Aethiopische%20Grammatik.%201886.%20%20Praetorius,%20Franz.%20%20Grammatica%20Aethiopica.%201886.%20%20Vittorio,%20Mariano.%20%20Chaldeae,%20seu%20Aethiopicae%20linguae%20institutiones.%201630.">Ge'ez Grammars Online</a></div>Courtesy of <a href="http://www.ancientbookshelf.com/">The Ancient Bookshelf</a><br /><blockquote><div class="post-header"> </div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: left;"><a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-9aM8OFfbYyM/V1iQ3jOQbJI/AAAAAAAACzc/KzjMswkclzwQ6hqfY0kXfso2BxyA1hXyQCLcB/s1600/Screen%2BShot%2B2016-06-08%2Bat%2B11.40.00%2BPM.png" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="200" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-9aM8OFfbYyM/V1iQ3jOQbJI/AAAAAAAACzc/KzjMswkclzwQ6hqfY0kXfso2BxyA1hXyQCLcB/s200/Screen%2BShot%2B2016-06-08%2Bat%2B11.40.00%2BPM.png" width="124" /></a></div><span style="font-size: x-small;">One can easily fit all of the Ge'ez grammars that have ever been  published in European languages on one shelf. &nbsp;Or, if you want to save  some of that shelf space for your <i>Wheel of Time</i> novels, you can  put most of those grammars on a flash drive/memory stick instead. &nbsp;Here  are some of the Ge'ez grammars that are available as PDFs (or in the  google books reader) online:<br /><br /><a href="https://archive.org/details/grammairethiop00chauoft" target="_blank">Chaîne, Marius. &nbsp;<i>Grammaire éthiopienne. </i>1907.</a><br /><br /><a href="https://archive.org/details/EthiopicethiopianLanguageGrammarByAugustDillmann" target="_blank">Dillman, August &amp; Carl Bezold. Trans. James A. Chrichton. &nbsp;<i>Ethiopic Grammar</i>. &nbsp;1907.</a><br /><br /><a href="https://archive.org/details/grammatikderthi00dillgoog" target="_blank">Dillman, August.<i>&nbsp;Grammatik der äthiopischen Sprache.&nbsp;</i>1857.</a><br /><br /><a href="https://archive.org/details/grammatikdert00dill" target="_blank">Dillman, August &amp; Carl Bezold. <i>Grammatik der äthiopischen Sprache.</i>&nbsp;1899.</a><br /><br /><a href="http://www.mdz-nbn-resolving.de/urn/resolver.pl?urn=urn:nbn:de:bvb:12-bsb10495466-1" target="_blank">Ludolf, Hiob. <i>Grammatica aethiopica</i>. 1661.</a><br /><br /><a href="https://archive.org/details/ethiopicgrammarw00merc" target="_blank">Mercer, Samuel. <i>Ethiopic Grammar, with Chrestomathy and Glossary. </i>1920.</a><br /><br /><a href="https://archive.org/details/thiopischegramm00praegoog" target="_blank">Praetorius, Franz. &nbsp;<i>Aethiopische Grammatik</i>. 1886.</a><br /><br /><a href="https://archive.org/details/grammaticaaethi00praegoog" target="_blank">Praetorius, Franz. &nbsp;<i>Grammatica Aethiopica. </i>1886.</a><br /><br /><a href="https://books.google.de/books/about/Chaldeae_seu_aethiopicae_linguae_institu.html?id=s9IWAAAAQAAJ&amp;redir_esc=y" target="_blank">Vittorio, Mariano. &nbsp;<i>Chaldeae, seu Aethiopicae linguae institutiones</i>. 1630</a>. </span></blockquote>]]></content>
